          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "LASER"
                ],
                "institute": "1USALRL"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Petawatt laser facility. 260 J of",
                "1.05 mu-m laser light, in a 450 fs long pulse, was",
                "focused onto a solid gold target, after being",
                "reflected from a plasma mirror. The focal spot size",
                "was 20 mu-m, producing an average intensity of",
                "greater than 10.E+20 W/cm2, corresponding to a",
                "ponderomotive energy of 3 MeV. A lower intensity",
                "prepulse of <100 mu-J was focused on the target 2 ns",
                "prior to the main pulse. The prepulse created a",
                "plasma at the target surface, which from a plasma",
                "hydrodynamic calculation is expected to have",
                "undergone a two-dimensional expansion with a rapidly",
                "decreasing plasma density extending away from the",
                "target. The density scale length is estimated to be",
                "50 mu-m, in which the main laser pulse experiences",
                "relativistic self-focusing or filamentation. The gold",
                "target was mounted on a cylindrical copper sample",
                "holder, which contained an additional quantity of",
                "197Au (0.3 g) and 238U ."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "BRST"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The low energy portion of the electron spectrum",
                "resembles a Maxwellian with a 3 MeV mean energy. The",
                "high energy tail extends up to 100 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "238U 1.2 g"
              ]
            }
          ],
